This project is a full-stack demonstration that scrapes real-time e-commerce data from FakeStoreAPI using Python, and displays it in a modern, responsive frontend UI. It features live product filtering, search, metadata summary, and category-based browsing â€” built for learning, demo, or portfolio purposes.

