ğŸš€ Features
ğŸ” Python Scraper (main.py)
Fetches product categories and product listings via REST API

Supports:

All products

Filter by category

JSON + CSV export

Includes timestamps and rating metadata

CLI-friendly and robust error handling

ğŸŒ Frontend (HTML + JS)
Loads data from ecommerce_data.json

Category filter (e.g., electronics, jewelry)

Product search functionality

Real-time product count and metadata display

Responsive design with modern UI (no frameworks!)

